62.6	Glenn_Greenwald	Glenn Greenwald	Glenn Greenwald (born March 6, 1967) is an American lawyer, columnist, blogger, and author. Greenwald worked as a constitutional and civil rights litigator before becoming a contributor (columnist and blogger) to Salon.com, where he focuses on political and legal topics. He has also contributed to other newspapers and political news magazines, including The New York Times, The Los Angeles Times, The Guardian, The American Conservative, The National Interest, and In These Times.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/0/00/Glenn_greenwald_portrait.jpg/200px-Glenn_greenwald_portrait.jpg
